<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Usage Limit Warning - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #fdcb6e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #d63031;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .usage-stats {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .usage-stats h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .usage-bar {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .usage-fill {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%);
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Usage Limit Warning</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>You're approaching your monthly usage limit for <%= limitType || 'posts' %>. Here's your current usage status:</p>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3><%= usagePercentage || '80' %>% of Monthly Limit Used</h3>
                <p>You've used <strong><%= used || '0' %></strong> out of <strong><%= limit || '0' %></strong> <%= limitType || 'posts' %> this month.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #d63031;"><strong>Only <%= remaining || '0' %> <%= limitType || 'posts' %> remaining!</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="usage-stats">
                <h3>Your Usage Breakdown</h3>
                <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                        <span>Posts:</span>
                        <span><strong><%= postsUsed || '0' %>/<%= postsLimit || '0' %></strong></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="usage-bar">
                        <div class="usage-fill" style="width: <%= postsPercentage || '0' %>%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                        <span>Comments:</span>
                        <span><strong><%= commentsUsed || '0' %>/<%= commentsLimit || '0' %></strong></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="usage-bar">
                        <div class="usage-fill" style="width: <%= commentsPercentage || '0' %>%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What happens when you reach the limit?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>You won't be able to generate new content until next month</li>
                <li>Your existing content remains accessible</li>
                <li>Limits reset automatically on <%= resetDate || 'the 1st of next month' %></li>
                <li>Upgrade to unlock unlimited usage</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Options to Continue:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Wait for monthly reset (in <%= daysUntilReset || 'X' %> days)</li>
                <li>Upgrade to a higher plan for more limits</li>
                <li>Purchase additional credits</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= upgradeUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Upgrade for Unlimited Usage â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Your usage limits will reset on <strong><%= resetDate || 'the 1st of next month' %></strong>. Plan your content accordingly!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

